<!--
NovaMenu contain group of Panel. Each Panel contain other control like buton, split button, combo
textbox, checkbox......

Controls
  +Attributes
    -text: Display text of button
    -orientation: Vertical or Horizontal. Default is horizontal
    -size: Large or Normal. Default is normal
    -toolTip: Display tooltip of button
    -showText: True or False. Default is True
    -showImage: True or False. Default is True
  +ChildNode
    -Image: Normal image of button 
    -LargeImage: Large image of button. If this node is null large image = image
-->
<RPBM_MENU title="RPBM">
